        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="section-label">About OHA</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">A technological oasis<br><em>on Bali's finest coast</em></h2>
          <p class="section-body">
            Ocean Hub Amed is not just a coworking space — it is a carefully designed environment where deep focus meets the raw beauty of the ocean. Set on Melasti Beach in Amed, northeast Bali, OHA spans more than 1,400 m² of premium workspace, coliving and lifestyle amenities, just 40 metres from the water's edge — with the sacred volcano Agung as a constant, dramatic backdrop.
          </p>
          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat">
