        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="section-label">Location</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Amed — Bali's<br><em>secret powerhouse</em></h2>
          <p class="section-body">While the rest of Bali buzzes with noise and crowds, Amed breathes differently. This quiet northeastern fishing village is renowned for its peace, deep Balinese culture, extraordinary coral reefs and, increasingly, for attracting focused remote workers who know that the best ideas emerge in stillness.</p>
          <div class="location-features">
            <div class="location-feature">
