            </div>
            <div class="location-feature">
              <div class="lf-dot"></div>
              <div class="lf-text"><strong>Mount Agung views</strong> — Bali's sacred volcano, dramatic sunsets every single evening from the terrace</div>
            </div>
            <div class="location-feature">
              <div class="lf-dot"></div>
              <div class="lf-text"><strong>World-class coral reefs</strong> — diving, snorkelling, paddle surf, fishing and kayaking at your door</div>
            </div>
            <div class="location-feature">
              <div class="lf-dot"></div>
              <div class="lf-text"><strong>Authentic Bali</strong> — temples, ceremonies and a community deeply connected to nature and Balinese culture</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="location-map reveal">
          <div>
            <p class="map-coords">8°20'45"S &nbsp;·&nbsp; 115°39'25"E</p>
