        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="section-label">Coliving</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Live where<br><em>you work best</em></h2>
          <p class="section-body">OHA is designed for professionals who want more than a desk. The coliving wing offers comfortable private and shared rooms within the same campus — so the distance from bed to desk is measured in footsteps. Networking happens naturally over coconuts at the jacuzzi or watching the volcano glow at sunset from the bamboo terrace.</p>
